column5: Good Day All,was informed this morning I had won this months contest for 1 year subscription to ESOX Magazine. You all need to enter these contests monthly and try and win some neat stuff.  So I thought I should go out and get a 649 for tonight.  Tight line and shark hooks  Ken
Yeah, I saw it HERE last night! Congrats to you. It's a great magazine. You'll love it.
Congrats !!! Amazing how fast that year will fly by.. just got my renewal notice in the mail today !
Congrats! A great magazine! I am sure your gonna love it!   G
Tremendous!  Going to be Just Swell!! and !  Shark hooks would be handy as well.
It's a great magazine!  My wife won a subscription last year....  We didn't win the lottery though....LOL
